&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Shell</title><link>https://0x13hrafnulf.github.io/notes/misc/shell/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://0x13hrafnulf.github.io/notes/misc/shell/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="shell-options">Shell Options&lt;/h1>
&lt;!-- Upgrade Shell -->
&lt;div class="note-card ">
&lt;div class="item">
&lt;h5 class="note-title">&lt;span>Upgrade Shell&lt;/span>&lt;/h5>
&lt;div class="card">
&lt;div class="card-body">&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>python -c 'import pty;pty.spawn(&amp;quot;/bin/bash&amp;quot;)&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Press &lt;code>CTRL+Z&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>stty raw -echo;fg&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>export TERM=xterm&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Check your terminal settings with &lt;code>stty -a&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Set columns and rows in upgraded shell to required ones
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>stty columns &amp;lt;cols&amp;gt;&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>stty rows &amp;lt;rows&amp;gt;&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>